  Home  Analyst Ratings  Analyst Activity – Deutsche Bank AG Reiterates Buy on Credit Suisse Group...     Analyst Ratings  Analyst Activity – Deutsche Bank AG Reiterates Buy on Credit Suisse Group (NYSE:CS)  ByME Staff -July 20, 2017 0  Share on Facebook
Tweet on Twitter


 Analyst Ratings For Credit Suisse Group (NYSE:CS)
Today, Deutsche Bank AG reiterated its Buy rating on Credit Suisse Group (NYSE:CS).
There are 1 sell rating, 7 buy ratings on the stock.
The current consensus rating on Credit Suisse Group (NYSE:CS) is Buy (Score: 2.75) with a consensus target price of $16.00 per share, a potential 5.40% upside.
Some recent analyst ratings include

7/20/2017-Deutsche Bank AG Reiterated Rating of Buy.
7/18/2017-Morgan Stanley Reiterated Rating of Buy.
6/26/2017-J P Morgan Chase & Co initiated coverage with a Overweight rating.
6/19/2017-Bank of America Corporation initiated coverage with a Buy rating.
3/7/2017-Citigroup Inc. Reiterated Rating of Buy.
1/31/2017-Keefe, Bruyette & Woods Upgrade from a “Market Perform ” rating to a ” Outperform” rating.
1/13/2017-Macquarie was Downgraded by analysts at Macquarie from a “Neutral ” rating to a ” Underperform” rating.

Dividend information for Credit Suisse Group (NYSE:CS)
Credit Suisse Group (NYSE:CS) pays an annual dividend of Community Ranking:  with a yield of 4.74% and an average dividend growth of 89.10% based on a 3 Year Average.
Dividend History for Credit Suisse Group (NYSE:CS)

On 5/1/2017 Credit Suisse Group announced a annual dividend of $0.70 4.6% with an ex dividend date of 5/8/2017 which will be payable on 5/26/2017.
On 4/13/2016 Credit Suisse Group announced a Annual dividend of $0.73 with an ex dividend date of 5/10/2016 which will be payable on 5/12/2016.
On 12/2/2015 Credit Suisse Group announced a … dividend of $0.48 with an ex dividend date of 12/10/2015 which will be payable on 12/21/2015.
On 5/9/2013 Credit Suisse Group announced a annual dividend of $0.11 0.36% with an ex dividend date of 5/1/2013 which will be payable on 5/13/2013.
On 4/3/2013 Credit Suisse Group announced a special dividend of $0.68 2.97% with an ex dividend date of 5/1/2013 which will be payable on 5/20/2013.



Recent Trading Activity for Credit Suisse Group (NYSE:CS)Shares of Credit Suisse Group closed the previous trading session at 15.18 up +0.10 0.63% with 1,660,734 shares trading hands. 
